52:52.294 --> 52:53.628
to visiting guests.

52:53.670 --> 52:55.046
That's the idea.

52:55.088 --> 52:57.090
And if our buyergoes for our proposal,

52:57.132 --> 53:01.303
your crafts and antiques willhave a home here year-round.

53:01.344 --> 53:02.721
So what do you think?

53:02.762 --> 53:05.891
I'd say we thinkit's all a great idea.

53:05.932 --> 53:07.142
Fantastic.

53:07.184 --> 53:08.393
Well, I'll need youall to be set up

53:08.393 --> 53:09.561
for our presentationto Niven.

53:09.561 --> 53:11.563
And we expect to see youall tomorrow at the-

53:11.605 --> 53:14.316
Ball, tomorrow night.

53:14.357 --> 53:16.693
We can't wait.

53:19.112 --> 53:23.408
Oh, we look forward to seeingyou take the first dance.

53:23.450 --> 53:25.994
Just like Grace and Arthurused to do.

53:29.206 --> 53:30.832
First dance?

53:30.874 --> 53:37.297
Well, we can't arguewith tradition, can we?

53:37.339 --> 53:39.299
Wait a second.

53:39.341 --> 53:43.970
Don't tell me that you are stillself-conscious about dancing.

53:44.012 --> 53:45.555
A little.

53:45.597 --> 53:49.559
Ok. How about a littlerefresher course?

53:56.441 --> 53:58.944
[plays music]

53:58.985 --> 54:00.779
♪

54:00.820 --> 54:03.365
May I have this dance?

54:03.406 --> 54:07.786
♪

54:07.786 --> 54:09.454
