54:13.792 --> 54:15.752
That's not my job.

54:15.794 --> 54:18.797
And anyway, when I dogo to fancy parties

54:18.797 --> 54:21.257
I'm there to schmooze donors.

54:21.299 --> 54:22.717
There's no time for dancing.

54:22.759 --> 54:23.635
Mmmhmm.

54:23.885 --> 54:28.348
