54:31.726 --> 54:35.605
[giggles]

54:35.647 --> 54:39.359
♪

54:51.830 --> 54:55.333
So um...

54:55.375 --> 54:56.668
I've got some thingsI wanna-

54:56.668 --> 54:59.587
No, no. I have- no, I do,because of the conference-

54:59.629 --> 55:00.630
That's right.

55:00.880 --> 55:03.800
The big conference callthat I need to prep for, so...

55:06.428 --> 55:07.220
Thanks for the dance.

55:07.262 --> 55:08.430
Yes. Yeah, yeah, yeah.

55:08.471 --> 55:09.764
I'll uh-

55:09.806 --> 55:10.598
Yeah, good luck.

55:10.640 --> 55:11.558
Thank you.

55:11.599 --> 55:13.393
Any time.

55:14.811 --> 55:15.854
Good-bye

