Hey. So, you and Lucy readyfor the ball?

55:29.659 --> 55:31.828
Yeah, yeah. I'd say so.

55:31.870 --> 55:33.705
Of course you realize,my friend,

55:33.747 --> 55:36.458
you now havea second chance.

55:36.499 --> 55:37.417
At what?

55:37.459 --> 55:38.376
Come on, Duncan.

55:38.626 --> 55:41.546
