55:55.727 --> 55:58.355
are back in eachother's lives now.

55:58.396 --> 56:01.566
But you'll never knowif you hold yourself back.

56:01.566 --> 56:02.984
Thanks.

56:06.738 --> 56:08.656
Thank you.

56:17.582 --> 56:19.417
Oh, Eleanor, thosesmell delicious.

56:19.459 --> 56:21.419
Will you put them over thereon the table for me please?

56:21.461 --> 56:22.295
You got it.

56:22.587 --> 56:23.421
Thank you. What do you thinkabout this here?

56:23.463 --> 56:24.547
Oh, perfect.

56:24.839 --> 56:27.842
Your aunt would be so proud ofeverything you've done here.

56:27.884 --> 56:29.052
Thank you.

56:29.094 --> 56:29.969
Lucy. You got a second?

56:30.261 --> 56:31.096
What is it? Niven's gonna behere any minute.

56:31.596 --> 56:32.972
I know, I know, I just wantto show you something.

56:33.014 --> 56:35.058
Ok.

