It looks amazing.

56:48.905 --> 56:49.989
Everything does.

56:50.281 --> 56:55.578
Oh yeah, and Eleanor even foundsome of Grace's old decorations.

56:55.620 --> 57:00.166
So, you feeling readyfor tonight?

57:00.208 --> 57:02.544
Yeah, I guess.

57:02.585 --> 57:05.588
