Everyone is staring.

01:04:29.407 --> 01:04:32.785
You're right, but I thinkthey're staring at me.

01:04:32.827 --> 01:04:36.122
Wondering how I got sucha beautiful dance partner.

01:04:36.163 --> 01:04:46.173
[classical music playing]♪

01:04:46.215 --> 01:04:54.181
[classical music playing]♪

01:04:54.223 --> 01:04:57.393
So you're due backin London next week.

01:05:01.063 --> 01:05:02.857
Well, I suppose everygood fairytale

01:05:02.898 --> 01:05:05.943
has to have an ending.

01:05:05.943 --> 01:05:07.903
Maybe.

01:05:07.945 --> 01:05:12.283
Being back here, I've rememberedsome history.

01:05:12.325 --> 01:05:14.410
What?

01:05:14.452 --> 01:05:18.372
How happy I used to be here.

01:05:18.414 --> 01:05:21.292
How happy I am now.

01:05:25.004 --> 01:05:26.088
[phone alert]

01:05:31.260 --> 01:05:32.011
What is it?

01:05:32.303 --> 01:05:34.221
Josephine's been texting.I missed it.

01:05:34.263 --> 01:05:34.889
Sorry, Duncan.

01:05:35.097 --> 01:05:37.183
I'll be back as soon as I can.

01:05:41.187 --> 01:05:42.605
[sheep baas]

01:05:51.656 --> 01:05:52.573
Josephine.

01:05:52.615 --> 01:05:54.742
I am so sorry I missedyour call.

01:05:54.784 --> 01:05:58.245
It was so noisy here I couldn'thear the phone ring.

01:05:58.287 --> 01:06:00.623
Lucy, are you ready?

01:06:00.665 --> 01:06:03.042
Yeah. For when?

01:06:03.084 --> 01:06:07.421
Uh... for now?

01:06:07.463 --> 01:06:11.050
Your conference callwith the trustees?

01:06:11.550 --> 01:06:13.969
[baaing]

01:06:14.011 --> 01:06:16.514
Hi everybody.

