Uh, Lucy, is that a sheepbehind you?

01:06:22.269 --> 01:06:23.771
Yep.

01:06:25.898 --> 01:06:29.318
And now I'd like to talk youthrough some numbers.

01:06:40.121 --> 01:06:42.164
How'd it go?

01:06:42.206 --> 01:06:46.210
Honestly... not great.

01:06:46.252 --> 01:06:47.128
I'm sorry.

01:06:47.169 --> 01:06:48.379
Between the sheep, the music,

01:06:48.421 --> 01:06:50.131
and keeping them waitingan hour,

01:06:50.172 --> 01:06:51.340
it was kind of a disaster.

01:06:51.382 --> 01:06:52.758
[laughs]

01:06:52.800 --> 01:06:58.681
But the good news is at leastI can finally relax now.

01:06:58.723 --> 01:07:00.558
How about a dance?

01:07:00.558 --> 01:07:03.185
That sounds great.

01:07:03.227 --> 01:07:06.105
Thank you for a trulywonderful evening.

01:07:06.147 --> 01:07:08.315
Let me read over your proposaland run the numbers

01:07:08.357 --> 01:07:12.153
and I'll have an answer for youby 8:30 tomorrow morning.

01:07:12.194 --> 01:07:13.362
Good night.

01:07:13.404 --> 01:07:14.613
Good night.

01:07:14.655 --> 01:07:16.615
Good night. After you.

01:07:19.368 --> 01:07:20.244
No pressure.

01:07:20.244 --> 01:07:22.621
No pressure at all.

01:07:31.255 --> 01:07:35.593
8:30, right on time.

01:07:35.593 --> 01:07:38.345
Duncan, whatever happens,

01:07:38.387 --> 01:07:39.638
I really wanna thank you

01:07:39.680 --> 01:07:42.141
for trying to do somethingnoble here

01:07:42.183 --> 01:07:46.437
and meeting me halfway.

01:07:46.437 --> 01:07:49.815
I would say we makea pretty great team.

01:07:56.489 --> 01:07:58.199
Great party last night.

01:07:58.240 --> 01:08:01.160
And I went over thenumbers afterwards.

01:08:01.202 --> 01:08:02.453
I like the property.

01:08:02.495 --> 01:08:05.289
Like the views,like the town.

01:08:05.331 --> 01:08:06.332
