01:09:25.536 --> 01:09:28.037
to do was go along with the plan.

01:09:28.080 --> 01:09:29.372
I told Niven that you would be

01:09:29.372 --> 01:09:30.707
presenting himwith a golf course.

01:09:30.707 --> 01:09:33.210
And we gave him one.And more.

01:09:33.252 --> 01:09:34.712
Look, Lucy and I thought that-

01:09:34.712 --> 01:09:36.380
You and Lucy?

01:09:36.380 --> 01:09:38.465
